<h2>Trackman Pro</h2>
<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span4 offset2">
    <section>
      <p>
        TrackMan Pro is the choice of the PGA Tour and R&A 
        for swing and ball flight analysis. A staple on professional 
        tours, with leading educators, club fitters, manufacturers 
        and players, TrackMan Pro is the industry standard for 
        accuracy, reliability and ease of use.
      </p>  
    </section>
  </div>  
  <div class="span4">
    <%= image_tag("TM-Shortgame.jpg", alt: "Trackman Golf", class: "img-rounded") %>    
  </div>  
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span4 offset2">
    <section>
      <p>
        TrackMan Pro measures and displays the full trajectory of any shot, from 6-foot pitches to 400-yard drives, 
        pinpointing the landing position with an accuracy of 1 
        foot at 100 yards. Delivering state-of-the-art data without 
        using any modeling, TrackMan Pro displays the shot's 
        actual 3D trajectory in real time together with all impact 
        and ball flight information.
      <p>
    </section>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <%= image_tag("Live-JustinRose.jpg", alt: "Justin Rose Live", class: "img-rounded") %>
  </div>
</div>
